      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it just feels like no matter what i do, the outcome is always the same. i try to fix things, i try to stay positive, i try to be better... but the universe just finds a way to reset me back to zero. it's not even about fixing it anymore, it's just the repetition of it all. i'm just so drained. it feels like a design flaw.",
